ygData.messageBody:
As you depart from the gates of felwithe, turn left and follow the zone
wall. The first zone you come to is Lesser faydark. The next zone (about 5
minute run) will be butcherblock.

-----Original Message-----
From: IF255@... [mailto:IF255@...]
Sent: Monday, April 19, 1999 6:26 PM
To: eq_wizards@onelist.com
Subject: [eq_wizards] Re: Places to Hunt (Some spoilers and rather long
txt)


From: IF255@...

Hello,
I was wondering if anyone would quickly mind telling me
where
ButcherBlock is, for i have never really traveled far from Felwithe and i
will soon be powerful enough to go hunting there. Thank you.

Zawel, High Elf wizard, Innoruuk server
